&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Position Summary&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Primary responsibility is setting up and controlling paper line filler equipment in a highly efficient manner.&amp;nbsp; The Evergreen technician will also ensure that all preventive maintenance items are performed correctly, and in a timely manner.&amp;nbsp; Corrective maintenance items must be aggressively addressed, using own technical skills and all other available resources.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential Functions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vigilantly monitor equipment operation for indications of impending problems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensures that all required preventive maintenance is performed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Addresses equipment problems in an aggressive manner, as to minimize downtime.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Makes controlled adjustments to equipment to optimize the running efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for maintaining documentation associated with operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Upholds highest quality, safety, and cleanliness standards within designated area.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicates with other team members to ensure efficient plant operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensures that all resources are available for production run.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Setup oncoming shift for successful run.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expected to perform any duties necessary to support the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Obtain information necessary to perform duties at pre shift team meetings, and by meeting with off going Serac Technician.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to learn complex systems and concepts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to make sound decisions in a timely fashion, under stressful situations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated mechanical skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to work on equipment in awkward positions, and reach difficult areas in the machine.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be willing and able to stay in confined work area wearing appropriate clean room attire for extended periods of time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be capable of wearing a full-face respirator.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable with operation of microprocessor-controlled equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable operating Microsoft Windows based applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong Communication skills: this position interacts frequently with other team members, other departments, management, and foreign nationals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
